reviewText: Almost as good as the first movie.
Very little nudity. Two or three women go topless once in each movies. Movies are ok, just don't expect some academy award movie. I wouldn't buy again if I knew what I know now when I bought it.

If you enjoyed the first 3 movies, here are the next 3. The last 2 are the ones the Up All Night never showed, so they made for a good first time showing. Still just as funny and politically incorrect as the others.

If your a big 90's comedy fan of high school/college/beach movies, then check this one out!  The vice academy movies are basically a combo of Police Academy and Charlie's Angels, except much sluttier and with a low-budget, but this is what makes it great. Part 4 and 5 are the best of the series, but Part 6 simply overstayed it's welcome. I highly recommend getting Volume 1 as Part 1 and 2 are even better. These movies are entertaining and funny! :)
